{"id":239359,"type":1,"name":"LOOP THE LOOP","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/03/73/239359_x5FMO.jpg","summary":"ある日突然【望んだ物が何でも手に入る】\r\n不思議な洋館に閉じ込められた高校生・レミは、\r\nそこで同じ境遇の11名の男女に出会う。彼らは互いを【家族】と呼び合い、\r\n館からの脱出を夢見て仲良く暮らしていた。\r\nだがそんな平穏な日々は一人の【家族】の死によって終わりを迎える。\r\n猜疑心膨らむ残された【家族】。犯人は誰か。事件の真相は?\r\n究極の飽和状態が生み出す、惨劇と絆の物語が幕を開ける。","info":"<li><span>作画: </span><a href=\"/person/15306\">カズミヤアキラ</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/10528\">月刊アクション</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>LOOP THE LOOP ～飽食の館～</li><li><span>出版社: </span>双葉社</li><li><span>发售日: </span>2018-01-12</li><li><span>原作: </span>Kate (sweet ampoule)</li><li><span>连载开始: </span>2017-06-24 (2017年8月号)</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"on_hold":2},"tags":[{"name":"游戏改","count":2},{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":15306,"image":"","name":"カズミヤアキラ","desc":"作画"},{"id":10528,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/65/5e/10528_prsn_0y48T.jpg","name":"月刊Action","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":111506,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/50/f8/111506_odr1d.jpg","title":"LOOP THE LOOP 飽食の館","type":"游戏","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/111506"},{"id":239362,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5f/2d/239362_Pxcpn.jpg","title":"LOOP THE LOOP 飽食の館","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/239362"}],"comic":[{"id":239361,"name":"LOOP THE LOOP (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/86/69/239361_pnnY4.jpg"},{"id":246551,"name":"LOOP THE LOOP (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/64/eb/246551_bwb4O.jpg"},{"id":293097,"name":"LOOP THE LOOP (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/2e/e5/293097_899ft.jpg"}]}